{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "5d461d89-140c-48ff-819b-40e7edd55dc0", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5d461d89-140c-48ff-819b-40e7edd55dc0@1.pkg/1772597509405/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597510238", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5d461d89-140c-48ff-819b-40e7edd55dc0@1.pkg/1772597509405/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597510238"}, "identifier": "5d461d89-140c-48ff-819b-40e7edd55dc0", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>①：“自制好物”利用回收材料制作物件，实现资源循环利用，减少废弃物产生，体现了节约资源的绿色理念，故①符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>②：“低碳点餐”按需点餐、剩余打包，避免食物浪费，符合绿色生活中节约资源的要求，故②符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>③：沉浸观剧属于文化消费，未直接体现资源节约或环保，故③不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>④：城市漫步通过步行减少碳排放，符合环保理念，故④不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025山西中考真题）绿色生活方式在年轻人中日益流行，这种方式既能减少资源消耗、降低环境负担，又能让他们在践行中收获内心的充实。下列属于绿色生活方式的是（ ）</p>\n\n<p>①自制好物 —— 用回收材料，动手制作实用家居物件</p>\n\n<p>②低碳点餐 —— 外出按需点餐，剩余打包避食物浪费</p>\n\n<p>③沉浸观剧 —— 入剧场观演，静享全新光影演出氛围</p>\n\n<p>④骑行漫游 —— 以单车代步，穿梭街巷品城市的烟火</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025山西中考真题）绿色生活方式在年轻人中日益流行，这种方式既能减少资源消耗、降低环境负担，又能让他们在践行中收获内心的充实。下列属于绿色生活方式的是（ ）①自制好物 —— 用回收材料，动手制作实用家居物件②低碳点餐 —— 外出按需点餐，剩余打包避食物浪费③沉浸观剧 —— 入剧场观演，静享全新光影演出氛围④骑行漫游 —— 以单车代步，穿梭街巷品城市的烟火", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/5d461d89-140c-48ff-819b-40e7edd55dc0@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754710505775", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②③</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①②④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>①③④</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>②③④</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编·2025山西中考真题）绿色生活方式在年轻人中日益流行，这种方式既能减少资源消耗、降低环境负担，又能让他们在践行中收获内心的充实。下列属于绿色生活方式的是（ ）</p>\n\n<p>①自制好物 —— 用回收材料，动手制作实用家居物件</p>\n\n<p>②低碳点餐 —— 外出按需点餐，剩余打包避食物浪费</p>\n\n<p>③沉浸观剧 —— 入剧场观演，静享全新光影演出氛围</p>\n\n<p>④骑行漫游 —— 以单车代步，穿梭街巷品城市的烟火</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "5d461d89-140c-4